  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A sphere of negative energy ripples out in a 60-foot radius from a point within range. Each creature in that area must make a Constitution saving throw. A target takes [[/r 8d6]] necrotic damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p><h3>Higher Levels</h3><p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 2d6]] for each slot level above 6th.</p><p><strong>Spell Lists.</strong> @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-journals.7iH4qANs2gxn0MIs.JournalEntryPage.NX28XQnco4pjOzF6]{Sorcerer}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-journals.7iH4qANs2gxn0MIs.JournalEntryPage.JsbrmCx9VF1Sizn8]{Warlock}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-journals.7iH4qANs2gxn0MIs.JournalEntryPage.5YX3k6END6NQWHOB]{Wizard}</p>",
